Package: causaltbl
Title: Tidy Causal Data Frames and Tools
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cory", "McCartan", email="cmccartan@g.harvard.edu", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Christopher T.", "Kenny", email="christopherkenny@fas.harvard.edu", role="aut"))
Description: Provides a 'causal_tbl' class for causal inference. A 'causal_tbl' 
    keeps track of information on the roles of variables like treatment and
    outcome, and provides functionality to store models and their fitted
    values as columns in a data frame.
Imports:
    rlang,
    cli,
    tibble (>= 3.0.0),
    tidyselect,
    vctrs,
    pillar,
    stats
Suggests: 
    dplyr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
